{"id":"api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator","title":"CheckboxRequiredValidator","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/forms\", \"name\": \"@angular/forms\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator\", \"name\": \"CheckboxRequiredValidator\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/forms\">@angular/forms</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L510-L550\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/15.0.1/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts#L510-L550\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"checkboxrequiredvalidator\">CheckboxRequiredValidator<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#checkboxrequiredvalidator\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label directive\">directive</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">该指令会借助 <code><a href=\"api/forms/NG_VALIDATORS\" class=\"code-anchor\">NG_VALIDATORS</a></code> 绑定把 <code>required</code> 验证器添加到任何带有 <code>required</code>\n属性的检查框控件上。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A Directive that adds the <code>required</code> validator to checkbox controls marked with the\n<code>required</code> attribute. The directive is provided with the <code><a href=\"api/forms/NG_VALIDATORS\" class=\"code-anchor\">NG_VALIDATORS</a></code> multi-provider list.</p>\n\n\n  </section>\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">参见<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/form-validation\">表单验证</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/form-validation\">Form Validation</a></p>\n</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n<h2 id=\"导出自\">导出自<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#导出自\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/forms/FormsModule\">\n      <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box\">FormsModule</code-example>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\">\n      <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box\">ReactiveFormsModule</code-example>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"selector-list\">\n  <h2 id=\"selectors\">选择器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#selectors\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><code>input[type=checkbox][required][<a href=\"api/forms/FormControlName\" class=\"code-anchor\">formControlName</a>]</code></li>\n    <li><code>input[type=checkbox][required][formControl]</code></li>\n    <li><code>input[type=checkbox][required][<a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a>]</code></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n  \n\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"inherited-members-list\">\n  <h3 id=\"继承自-requiredvalidator\">继承自 <code><a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/forms/RequiredValidator\">RequiredValidator</a></code><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#继承自-requiredvalidator\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li>\n      <code><a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/forms/RequiredValidator#required\"><span class=\"property-binding\">@Input()</span><br><span class=\"member-name\">required</span>: boolean | string</a></code>\n    </li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n  \n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"description\">\n    <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    \n    <h3 id=\"adding-a-required-checkbox-validator-using-template-driven-forms\" translation-result=\"on\">使用模板驱动表单为复选框添加必填项验证器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#adding-a-required-checkbox-validator-using-template-driven-forms\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3><h3 translation-origin=\"off\">Adding a required checkbox validator using template-driven forms<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#adding-a-required-checkbox-validator-using-template-driven-forms\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">下面的例子展示了如何为一个带有 ngModel 绑定的检查框添加必填项验证器。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The following example shows how to add a checkbox required validator to an input attached to an*\nngModel binding.</p>\n\n<code-example>\n&lt;input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"active\" <a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a> required&gt;\n</code-example>\n\n  </section>\n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/FormsModule\n - api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#adding-a-required-checkbox-validator-using-template-driven-forms\n - api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#checkboxrequiredvalidator\n - api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#description\n - api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#see-also\n - api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#selectors\n - api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#使用模板驱动表单为复选框添加必填项验证器\n - api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#导出自\n - api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#继承自-requiredvalidator\n - api/forms/FormControlName\n - api/forms/FormsModule\n - api/forms/NG_VALIDATORS\n - api/forms/NgModel\n - api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\n - api/forms/RequiredValidator\n - api/forms/RequiredValidator#required\n - guide/form-validation\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L510-L550\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/15.0.1/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts#L510-L550\n-->"}